title: US Olympic Gold Medalists hometowns, USA, 2008
name: US Olympic Gold Medalists hometowns, USA, 2008
description: This Dataset shows the birthplaces of Olympic Gold Medal Winners from the US, who competed for the US. This dataset isn't perfect, and is definitely missing a number of athletes, but its a pretty good sample size. For example, it doesn't have any of the hometowns for the 2004 Gold Medal Winning rowers. Also, if there were multiple athletes from the same City, For example, Chicago, IL. Only one point is shown on that city. If you want a better idea on which state has the most Olympic gold medalists, i will post the number of gold medalists by state.  Data was geocoded based on information from wikipedia, found here:http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Olympic_gold_medalists_for_the_United_States
